Superman and Lois, the last remnant of the fallen Arrowverse, returns for its 3rd season. The series manages to up the stakes with some major plot points, huge character introductions, and changes to the status quo but does it help or hurt the series overall? Hear us dissect this season of Superman and Lois and discuss what future DC projects can learn from this version of Superman on this episode of the Major Issues Podcast.  
  
Please leave us a **_review_** on [**ITunes**](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us wherever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our merchandise! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by **ComicBook Clique**, the only stop for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media.  

